# VEHICLE::ROLL_UP_WINDOW

## Summary
Rolls up a given vehicle window. NB - it only snaps the window up. Probably want to do this off-screen

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **SC_WINDOW_LIST** windowNumber

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
windowIndex:
0 = Front Left Window
1 = Front Right Window
2 = Rear Left Window
3 = Rear Right Window
4 = Front Windscreen
5 = Rear Windscreen
6 = Mid Left
7 = Mid Right
8 = Invalid
